# Fix Rope Climbing Logic & Stuck Key

## Summary
- **Fixed Rope X-Alignment**: Increased engaging distance to 10px.
- **Fixed Climb Down**: Correctly selects "Down" key at rope top.
- **Improved Completion Detection**: Implemented "Wiggle Test" to confirm platform arrival.
- **Fixed Movement Oscillation**: Corrected distance calculation in horizontal movement logic.
- **Fixed Key Stuck**: Ensured UP/DOWN keys are released after climbing.

## Changes

### 1. Fix Rope Key Stuck (Accidental Grabbing)
**File**: [Services/CharacterMovementController.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs)

**Problem**: User reported character accidentally grabbing adjacent ropes after finishing a climb.
**Cause**: The [ClimbRopeAsync](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs#641-875) method exited its loop (upon reaching target) but didn't reliably release the climb key or reset the controller's internal `_currentPressedKey` state. The key remained logically "pressed".
**Fix**: Updated the `finally` block to call [StopMovement()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs#347-367) which forces a complete state reset and key release.

```csharp
finally
{
    // Ensure all keys are released and internal state is reset
    StopMovement();
    
    // Safety net: Explicitly release common climb keys
    SendKeyInput(VK_UP, true);
    SendKeyInput(VK_DOWN, true);
    SendKeyInput(VK_MENU, true);
}
```

### 2. Move Oscillation Fix
**File**: [Services/CharacterMovementController.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs)
- Changed [MoveToTargetAsync](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs#200-331) to use horizontal distance (`Math.Abs(dx)`) instead of euclidean distance. This prevents "Long Press" (Running) when vertically distant but horizontally close, stopping the Left/Right oscillation.

### 3. Active Rope Exit Check (Wiggle Test)
**File**: [Services/CharacterMovementController.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/CharacterMovementController.cs)
- Added logic to move Right when near top of rope. If X changes, climb is done.

## Verification
- **Rope**: Character climbs to top, performs Wiggle Test (optional), then immediately releases UP key. Passing by other ropes does not trigger grab.
- **Movement**: Character aligns X smoothly without jitter.
